content: I decided to give this app a chance, and within 2 minutes I had buyers remorse. All the info in this can easily searched for in google for free and get more info on location and spawns like what the weather needs to be to even see the spawn.
It's great BUT.. I honestly can't believe that it keeps crashing right after I used it... I really want a refund at this point.

This is really good, it helps with finding pokemon you need to build a fun team. My only real question for the devs is if they will update the app for both the dlcs when they come out? The isle of armor is out and there is nothing on the app. Edit: The devs are planning on adding the dlc pokedex expansions i just didnt read far enough.
Just not good. Lack of function in comparison to free apps.

Would be 5 star , but really only gives you half of what you're looking for in a PokeDex. App doesn't actually show you pictures of the pokemon, like you can find in other FREE apps. Doesn't give you the ability to Mark if the pokemon has been caught. The app does show you Text information as to where you can find said pokemon but a map would be perfect, especially since you're paying for it. ALL-IN-ALL this is a good and quick way to look up a pokemon found in the Galar Region. Will Make 5* WU.
Had a problem. It's fixed now. Very easy to use and much better then looking up the pokedex on any website.
replyContent: Hi Eric, we are glad your problem is resolved! Thank you for your kind feedback! We are committed to bringing more features and updates in the coming months!
